{% comment %}
  CUSTOM · Hero V2 — new homepage hero, replaces the image-banner-clone hero
  from decision 012. Fully hardcoded content (settings: []), see decision 031.
  Copy is locale-gated IT/EN/FR (decision 024 pattern) since there is no
  existing translation to reuse for this new design.
{% endcomment %}
{{ 'custom-hero-v2.css' | asset_url | stylesheet_tag }}

{%- liquid
  assign is_en = false
  assign is_fr = false
  if request.locale.iso_code == 'en'
    assign is_en = true
  elsif request.locale.iso_code == 'fr'
    assign is_fr = true
  endif
-%}

<div class="custom-hero-v2 color-scheme-4 gradient">
  <div class="custom-hero-v2__overlay" aria-hidden="true"></div>

  <div class="custom-hero-v2__inner page-width">
    <div class="custom-hero-v2__intro">
      <p class="custom-hero-v2__overline scroll-trigger animate--slide-in">
        {%- if is_en -%}
          THE TRUCKER'S SHOES
        {%- elsif is_fr -%}
          LES CHAUSSURES DU CAMIONNEUR
        {%- else -%}
          LE SCARPE DEL CAMIONISTA
        {%- endif -%}
      </p>

      <h1 class="custom-hero-v2__heading scroll-trigger animate--slide-in">
        {%- if is_en -%}
          WORK BETTER.<br>LIVE BETTER.
        {%- elsif is_fr -%}
          TRAVAILLEZ MIEUX.<br>VIVEZ MIEUX.
        {%- else -%}
          LAVORA MEGLIO.<br>VIVI MEGLIO.
        {%- endif -%}
      </h1>

      <p class="custom-hero-v2__subheading scroll-trigger animate--slide-in">
        {%- if is_en -%}
          Sneaker comfort. S3S protection. On in 2 seconds. <strong>Handmade in Italy</strong> for those who live the road every day.
        {%- elsif is_fr -%}
          Confort de sneaker. Protection S3S. Enfilez et partez en 2 secondes. <strong>Fabriquées à la main en Italie</strong> pour ceux qui vivent la route au quotidien.
        {%- else -%}
          Comfort da sneaker. Protezione da S3S. Infili e vai in 2 secondi. <strong>Fatte a mano in Italia</strong> per chi vive la strada ogni giorno.
        {%- endif -%}
      </p>
    </div>

    {%- comment -%}
      The image sits between the copy and the feature list in the DOM on purpose. On
      mobile it is an in-flow band: as a full-bleed background it was always underneath
      the text, so the shoe could never be seen whole. From 750px up the CSS lifts it
      back out of flow into a background, where the copy occupies a column beside it and
      no longer covers it.

      <picture> because this is art direction, not resizing: mobile gets the in-context
      workshop shot, desktop the studio profile shot (square, on pure black).
    {%- endcomment -%}
    <picture class="custom-hero-v2__picture">
      <source
        media="(min-width: 1100px)"
        srcset="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0960/9527/3303/files/scarpa-profilo-landing-cropped.jpg?v=1775983178"
        width="3501"
        height="3501"
      >
      <img
        src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0960/9527/3303/files/hero_image.png?v=1783857445"
        alt=""
        width="941"
        height="1672"
        class="custom-hero-v2__media"
        loading="eager"
        fetchpriority="high"
        aria-hidden="true"
      >
    </picture>

    <div class="custom-hero-v2__details">
      <ul class="custom-hero-v2__features" role="list">
        <li class="custom-hero-v2__feature scroll-trigger animate--slide-in" data-cascade>
          <span class="custom-hero-v2__feature-check" aria-hidden="true">{{ 'icon-checkmark.svg' | inline_asset_content }}</span>
          <span class="custom-hero-v2__feature-text">
            <strong>{%- if is_en -%}PATENTED FAST WEAR{%- elsif is_fr -%}FAST WEAR BREVETÉ{%- else -%}FAST WEAR BREVETTATO{%- endif -%}</strong>
            <span>{%- if is_en -%}On your feet in 1 second{%- elsif is_fr -%}Enfilées en 1 seconde{%- else -%}Le indossi in 1 secondo{%- endif -%}</span>
          </span>
        </li>
        <li class="custom-hero-v2__feature scroll-trigger animate--slide-in" data-cascade>
          <span class="custom-hero-v2__feature-check" aria-hidden="true">{{ 'icon-checkmark.svg' | inline_asset_content }}</span>
          <span class="custom-hero-v2__feature-text">
            <strong>{%- if is_en -%}MAXIMUM SAFETY{%- elsif is_fr -%}SÉCURITÉ MAXIMALE{%- else -%}SICUREZZA MASSIMA{%- endif -%}</strong>
            <span>EN ISO 20345:2022+A1:2024</span>
          </span>
        </li>
        <li class="custom-hero-v2__feature scroll-trigger animate--slide-in" data-cascade>
          <span class="custom-hero-v2__feature-check" aria-hidden="true">{{ 'icon-checkmark.svg' | inline_asset_content }}</span>
          <span class="custom-hero-v2__feature-text">
            <strong>MADE IN ITALY</strong>
            <span>{%- if is_en -%}100% handmade{%- elsif is_fr -%}100 % fabriquées à la main{%- else -%}100% fatte a mano{%- endif -%}</span>
          </span>
        </li>
        <li class="custom-hero-v2__feature scroll-trigger animate--slide-in" data-cascade>
          <span class="custom-hero-v2__feature-check" aria-hidden="true">{{ 'icon-checkmark.svg' | inline_asset_content }}</span>
          <span class="custom-hero-v2__feature-text">
            <strong>{%- if is_en -%}INDESTRUCTIBLE{%- elsif is_fr -%}INDESTRUCTIBLES{%- else -%}INDISTRUTTIBILI{%- endif -%}</strong>
            <span>{%- if is_en -%}1095 working days guaranteed{%- elsif is_fr -%}1095 jours de travail garantis{%- else -%}Garantite 1095 giorni di lavoro{%- endif -%}</span>
          </span>
        </li>
      </ul>

      <div class="custom-hero-v2__ctas scroll-trigger animate--slide-in">
        <a href="#acquista" class="button button--primary custom-hero-v2__cta">
          {%- if is_en -%}BUY NOW{%- elsif is_fr -%}ACHETER{%- else -%}ACQUISTA ORA{%- endif -%}
        </a>
        <a href="#intro" class="button button--secondary custom-hero-v2__cta">
          {%- if is_en -%}LEARN MORE{%- elsif is_fr -%}EN SAVOIR PLUS{%- else -%}SCOPRI DI PIÙ{%- endif -%}
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

{% schema %}
{
  "name": "CUSTOM · Hero V2",
  "tag": "section",
  "class": "custom-hero-v2-section",
  "settings": [],
  "presets": [
    {
      "name": "CUSTOM · Hero V2"
    }
  ]
}
{% endschema %}
